Download Terraform for Windows

ON Web Browser https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install

Under Windows, select :

Architecture: 64-bit

It will download a .zip file (example: terraform_1.9.8_windows_amd64.zip).

Extract the ZIP File

Right-click on the downloaded ZIP → Extract All

Move this terraform.exe to a permanent location

for example :

C:\Terraform

Add Terraform to System PATH

Press Windows + R, type sysdm.cpl → press Enter

Go to Advanced → click Environment Variables

Under System Variables, find Path, select it → click Edit

Click New → add the path where terraform.exe is located

Click OK

Verify Installation

Open Command Prompt

terraform -version

# You see
Terraform v1.13.4
on windows_386
